commit message: Fixes class cast issue when reading text from Clipboard. https://github.com/frostwire/frostwire-android/issues/67
Fixes issue when trying to create Application Storage directory https://github.com/frostwire/frostwire-android/issues/66

Icon Refresh

Refreshing main_menu_button, back_icon_activity, and the player icons.
Since they were always appearing bigger on screen than what I thought,
I am providing icons in 48x48 size just as the default icon size for
drawable-hdpi on android.

New Icons

Icons include favoriting a song and the context menu for the action
bar.
